reviewText: It's the best tape ever released out of the Rugrats TV Series!!!!!!!!!
I love this one we still have this one

You get what you pay for, literally! Very poor quality! You can't even watch the movie for grey lines going across the screen. Would not purchase again. The only reason I did not return for a refund is to avoid the hassle. NEVER AGAIN.

It's a great video for kids to learn about the bath tub and that it's not so bad and nothing will happen to you! My niece and newphew kinda like Rugrats so it was a good tape to get for them!! They kinda grew out of it however!
